\par 
\par {\*\atrfstart 441950227}ALEXANDER SELKIRK had his Daniel Defoe to immortalize him and the island of Juan Fernandez, and in every man's memory lingers the delights of hours spent with Robinson Crusoe wandering over his little empire with his man Friday 
and his parrot and goats, but the chronicler of the weary months and years of waiting spent by a lone Indian woman on San Clemente island, off the southern coast of California, is yet to come.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs15\fs16\insrsid11564503 {\*\atrfend 441950227}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 441950227}{\*\atndate -2025738792}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar
