\ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid11564503 \chatn }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11564503 Girl Crusoe}}}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2914953 
\par 
\par It has been many years since she was found and taken to a hospitable home in Santa Barbara, and still no one has taken her wonderful experience as the theme for a novel, nor has San Clemente island achieved notice because of her habitation thereon for eig
hteen years in solitude. Along the southern coast of the State this island is better known as the {\*\atrfstart 441950228}Island of Skulls}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af31507\afs16 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs15\fs16\insrsid3605128 {\*\atrfend 441950228}{\*\atnid SS}{\*\atnauthor 
Sara Schwebel}\chatn {\*\annotation{\*\atnref 441950228}{\*\atndate -2025738764}\ltrpar \pard\plain \ltrpar\s16\ql \li0\ri0\sa160\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0\itap0\contextualspace \rtlch\fcs1 
